name: The user is presented with error message for code with invalid syntax in tryEditor for Find Numbers with Even Number of Digits

steps.name: Given  The user is on Question page of "Find Numbers with Even Number of Digits" after logged in
When  The user enter python code with invalid syntax in tryEditor from sheet "pythonCode" and 1
And  The user clicks on run button
Then  The user should be presented with error message as "SyntaxError: bad input on line 1"
